Package xyz.swatt.selenium

SWATT's Selenium package will help with testing Web Apps.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    WebDriverTransitionalWrapper
    This Class extends WebDriverWrapper and contains all of it's functionality.
    WebDriverWrapper
    This class is a wrapper for the Selenium WebDriver class.
    WebElementTransitionalWrapper
    This Class extends WebElementWrapper and contains all of it's functionality.
    WebElementWrapper
    This class is a wrapper for the Selenium WebElement class.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    WebDriverWrapper.BrowserType

    A list of supported Google Chrome Web Browsers.
    WebDriverWrapper.FirefoxBrowser
    A list of supported Firefox Web Browsers.
    WebDriverWrapper.FirefoxExtension
    All known Firefox Extensions.
    WebDriverWrapper.IEBrowser
    A list of supported Internet Explored (IE) Web Browsers.

Package xyz.swatt.selenium Description

SWATT's Selenium package will help with testing Web Apps. It contains Selenium Wrapper Classes that should be used instead of the Selenium Classes.
